The ASUCD Business Manager oversees the day to day operations of ASUCD.

The current ASUCD Business Manager is Brett Burns. He previously served as interim ASUCD Business Manager. Prior to Brett, Geoff Straw served as interim ASUCD Business Manager while simultaneously continuing his position as the Director of Unitrans. Mark Champagne was the longtime ASUCD Business Manager who retired in June 2011 after 32 years of dedication to the Association.
